  "texts": [
    "When a summary's bullet covers a reference insight, we can compare generated citations to this reference set of cites.",
    "For each partially or fully covered reference insight, cited documents are extracted from the paired summary bullet point using a regular expression ([.",
    "*]), and we measure the precision and recall between the generated and gold-standard cites.",
    "The Citation Score of a reference insight is calculated as the F1 score of the precision and recall, giving equal weight to both.",
    "In short, a system must be both precise and thorough in its citing to achieve a high Citation Score."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}